(141, 1, '2020-07-13 20:31:22', '2020-07-13 20:31:22', '<h2>Discover Your Purpose So You Can Ignite Your Passion And Fulfill Your Potential</h2>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Join Us Now\n					</a>\n			<h2>What I Offer\n</h2>		\n				<h3>\n					SPEAKER\n				</h3>\n								<p>Powerful and uplifting keynotes that will reignite your passion and help you gain clarity on your path.<br><br></p>\n				<h3>\n					COACH\n				</h3>\n								<p>Group and individualized coaching programs to provide structure, support and accountability to achieve your lifes goals and desires.</p>\n				<h3>\n					AUTHOR\n				</h3>\n								<p>Author of the book Dare To Color Outside The Lines and companion Readers Guide.<br><br><br></p>\n										<img src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/DrNoja-1-683x1024-1-osey0ndwkp2lro9lhs9sd01l03v8cskzaajjid648w.jpg\" title=\"DrNoja-1-683&#215;1024\" alt=\"DrNoja-1-683x1024\" />											\n			<h2>My Story</h2>		\n		<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dr. Enojare Tina Uadiale Ph.D (also known as Rev. Noja) is an ordained and licensed minister from Shiloh Church in Oakland.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">She is an accomplished Motivational Speaker, Life Coach and is happily married to her husband, Prof. Michael Uadiale (CPA, CGMA, Ph.D) with whom she started and Pastored the Shiloh African Fellowship before the Lord directed them to start the Kingdom Builders Ministry also in Shiloh.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Vision for this ministry is to raise up champions in various vocations and businesses who will showcase Godly Success, Character, Integrity, and Biblical Prosperity. The goal as such is to build covenant people of faith through Equipping, Encouraging and Empowerment so they can become relevant in the market place.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						 Read More...\n					</a>\n			<h2>Book Your Coaching Call With Dr. Noja</h2>		\n		<h3>Click below to schedule a complimentary introductory call to discuss whats going on with you and explore how I can help you identify your potential and get realigned on your path.</h3>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Call Now\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/163.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/163.jpg 1920w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/163-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/163-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/163-768x512.jpg 768w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/163-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />											\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"188\" src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/advice-01-Medium-300x188-1.png\" alt=\"\" />											\n			<h2>Dare To Color Outside The Lines</h2>		\n		<h3>This book has the power to change your life. Supported by scripture, you will feel encouraged and inspired to confidently pursue your destiny and regain a passion for life.</h3>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						 Grab Your Copy Today\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iconrocket1.png\" alt=\"\" />											\n			<h2>The Ignite Mentorship Program</h2>		\n		<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">This powerful 6-week group coaching program will put you firmly on the path to fulfilling your destiny. Click below to learn more and apply.</h3><h3></h3>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Join Now\n					</a>\n			<h2>Testimonials</h2>		\n							<p style= \"position:absolute;margin-top:160px;\">Thank you so much for this excellent gift to the Christian world. Dr Noja Uadiale has given us an encouraging book to ponder upon. This book will change the way you think. It\'s a must-read for anyone searching or trying to fulfill their God-given destiny in life.<p>\n							<img src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/66593667AndrewFan-osf3s82mcr6vphehk5s2qtmsx90v5dhrb09sa9cq4c.jpg\" title=\"66593667AndrewFan\" alt=\"66593667AndrewFan\" />						\n														<p style = \"margin-top : -18px;margin-left:10px;\">Dr. Andrew Faniku</p>\n						<i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i> 5/5		\n							<p style= \"position:absolute;margin-top:160px;\">Awesome book! totally love it. Not bulky and easy to read and understand. I love the perspective of seeing problems as challenges and opportunities. Breaking down the process of the bridge between the promise and the prize.<p>\n							<img src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/PASTOR-BUNMI-OLANIRAN-osf67audh8e590x23asv8cl219tz7y6kxzy3s28rp8.jpg\" title=\"PASTOR-BUNMI-OLANIRAN\" alt=\"PASTOR-BUNMI-OLANIRAN\" />						\n														<p style = \"margin-top : -18px;margin-left:10px;\">Pastor Bunmi Olaniran</p>\n						<i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i> 5/5		\n							<p style= \"position:absolute;margin-top:160px;\">A wonderful book by Dr Noja Uadiale, I found myself fully immersed in the biblical truths that unfolded as I turned from one page to another<p>\n							<img src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/ELIUD-NDUTI-osf6cytcoa5d8eos08ywrf42xvwmm9oc21igx3uc70.jpg\" title=\"ELIUD-NDUTI\" alt=\"ELIUD-NDUTI\" />						\n														<p style = \"margin-top : -18px;margin-left:10px;\">Eliud Nduti</p>\n						<i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i><i>&#xE934;</i> 5/5		\n							<p style= \"position:absolute;margin-top:160px;\">What I love about this book is that Dr.Noja explains powerful Christian principles that you can apply practically into your life- without any added fluff.<p>\n							<img src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/jennifer-1