(162, 1, '2020-07-13 22:26:04', '2020-07-13 22:26:04', '<h2>About</h2>		\n										<img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DrNoja-1-683x1024-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DrNoja-1-683x1024-2.jpg 683w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DrNoja-1-683x1024-2-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" />											\n			<h2>Dr. Noja Uadiale</h2>		\n		<p>My path to becoming a coach and mentor was the most natural thing for me. Ever since I was a young child it has been my desire to help and elevate people and my siblings related to me as a mother figure rather than a sister.</p><p>It is my instinct to play a maternal and guiding role, so it was no surprise to me when young women in my church were drawn to me and asked me to mentor them. This marked the beginning of my formal role as a coach. I mentored ten young women through a variety of personal and professional challenges and as a result of this transformative process, many went on to get married and make pivotal changes in their careers leading to great professional success.</p><p>It is my great passion to teach, coach and mentor because I believe that our purpose as human beings is to touch and make a difference in peoples lives. I believe that in every encounter with someone there should be a deposit of value. There are no ordinary encounters. Each interaction is an opportunity to make a powerful positive impact.</p><p>Because of this passion, I am committed to delivering phenomenal results for my clients. I will be a pillar to help you take the steps and create the changes that will enable you to identify and fulfill your purpose and awaken your passion</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n										Contact Me\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n			<h2>FOLLOW ME</h2>		\n							<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Facebook-f\n									</a>\n							<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Linkedin-in\n									</a>\n							<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n					Amazon\n									</a>', 'about', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2020-07-13 23:37:29', '2020-07-13 23:37:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/elementor/?page_id=162', 0, 'page', '', 0),
