(184, 1, '2020-07-13 23:18:24', '2020-07-13 23:18:24', '<h2>Coaching\n</h2>		\n			<h3>Which coaching is right for you?</h3>		\n			<h2>Individual One-On-One Coaching:</h2>		\n		<h3>Individual coaching is the right fit for you if you want a more personalized approach and thrive on a deeper dive into your current challenges and goals. If you need more support right now and want to feel like someone is by your side every step of the way, then individual coaching is the way to go.</h3><p>Its also the best choice if youre experiencing a crisis or a major life change. After our initial complimentary phone call I will create a custom coaching package for you that will best fit your needs and desires. For most clients this consists of one or two 60-minute or 30-minute weekly phone calls and can also include daily messaging and check-ins.</p>		\n										<img width=\"800\" height=\"468\" src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3629604-e1589493144119-1024x599.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3629604-e1589493144119-1024x599.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3629604-e1589493144119-300x175.jpg 300w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3629604-e1589493144119-768x449.jpg 768w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/3629604-e1589493144119.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" />											\n		<blockquote><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Your vision will become clear only when you can look into your own heart. Who looks outside, dreams; who looks inside, awakes.  Carl Jung</p></blockquote>		\n			<h2>Group Coaching\n</h2>		\n										<img width=\"800\" height=\"620\" src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4801-e1589493483217-1024x793.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4801-e1589493483217-1024x793.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4801-e1589493483217