00x232.jpg 300w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4801-e1589493483217-768x595.jpg 768w, http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/4801-e1589493483217.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" />											\n		<p>Group coaching is the right fit for you if you enjoy the dynamic interaction of a group and a sense of community. My group coaching and mentorship program<a href=\"https://ignite.drnoja.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><b>Ignite</b></a>is a 6-week online coaching program that will help you identify your passion so you can achieve your deepest goals and live in alignment with your lifes purpose. This program will give you the structure, accountability and support that you need to make your dreams from something you just think about to your new reality.</p><p>To learn more about the program and apply go to. Spots are limited to 12 people to keep the group intimate and ensure everyone gets the personalized attention they need.</p>		\n										<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/elementor/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iconrocket1.png\" alt=\"\" />											\n			<h2>The Ignite Mentorship Program</h2>		\n		<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">This powerful 6-week group coaching program will put you firmly on the path to fulfilling your destiny. Click below to learn more and apply.</h3><h3></h3>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Join Now\n					</a>', 'coaching', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '142-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-13 23:28:07', '2020-07-13 23:28:07', '', 142, 'http://localhost/elementor/index.php/2020/07/13/142-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
